fields.Title: WHIRLING F2 / CUNO WAKEUP
fields.Description: If you didn't make the authority check.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah? What? What bells?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah? What? What bells?"

fields.Title: You: ""*Something*.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "*Something*."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah, like what?" He seems to like..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, like what?" He seems to like the idea.

fields.Title: Empathy: "Wow, he did not take that rejection..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Wow, he did not take that rejection well.

fields.Title: You: ""I'm in pain, what... happened?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm in pain, what... happened?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Babybeard was in here. Was probabl..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Babybeard was in here. Was probably a *bitch* to clean this shit up..." This seems to please him.

fields.Title: You: ""I'm a psycholocomotor, Cuno.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm a psycholocomotor, Cuno."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Some doctor your pig friends sent..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Some doctor your pig friends sent over. Nix Fucklieb, I think. Total cunt." He spits on the ground. "Came in here and knife fucked you, when you where sleeping. Then fucked off and told me to phone him if you shit yourself."

fields.Title: You: ""I feel fantastic. Let's... rock.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I feel fantastic. Let's... rock."

fields.Title: You: ""Who cares. Who cares about me. It..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Who cares. Who cares about me. It doesn't matter."

fields.Title: You: ""What style was that?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What style was that?"

fields.Title: Composure: "Cunn and Pig? And you're picking hi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Cunn and Pig? And you're picking him up on your cop-frequency too. This is... bad.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Nix Fucklieb, I think he was calle..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Nix Fucklieb, I think he was called," he says trying to remember the situation. "Said he was a doctor. Then fucked off and told me to phone him if you shit yourself."

fields.Title: You: ""Do you know if Joyce -- the compan..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Do you know if Joyce -- the company lady with the boat -- is alright?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""The big fuckhole?" There's a flash..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The big fuckhole?" There's a flash of respect on his freckled face. "Yeah, he's drinking downstairs. Cuno's not into that."

fields.Title: You: ""Okay.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay."

fields.Title: You: ""Thanks for your help, Cuno." (Conc..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Thanks for your help, Cuno." (Conclude.)

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Shit, pig... You better have some..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Shit, pig... You better have some more shit than fuckin' roses or something."

fields.Title: Conceptualization: "Big-up fucky-fingers? He *is* a *fr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Big-up fucky-fingers? He *is* a *free-thinker*. Beyond the box. Can't argue with that.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Thanks, pig." He quickly glances a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Thanks, pig." He quickly glances at you, then looks away. "Now get your crippled ass up and tell Cuno, what are we gonna do now?"

fields.Title: Composure: "The kid really doesn't seem to harb..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The kid really doesn't seem to harbour any animosity towards you. He seems almost friendly.

fields.Title: You: ""We're cool, Cuno,""
fields.Dialogue Text: "We're cool, Cuno,"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Nah... Cuno's just off speed for a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Nah... Cuno's just off speed for a few days..." There's a melancholy look in his eyes.

fields.Title: You: ""Are you hurt?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Are you hurt?"

fields.Title: Cuno: "You see the shape of a prepubescent..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You see the shape of a prepubescent boy in FALN pants. It turns double -- then triple -- from the pain. He says:
fields.Alternate1: You see Cuno's familiar shape in the FALN pants. It turns double -- then triple -- from the pain. He says:

fields.Title: Empathy: "Wow... Cuno's about to take pity on..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Wow... Cuno's about to take pity on you. That's unexpected.

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "Yeah, that kid's taken a beating --..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Yeah, that kid's taken a beating -- or ten -- from his dad. He has regard for a man who can walk after taking some damage.

fields.Title: Hand/Eye Coordination: "It probably is... fucking butterfin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It probably is... fucking butterfingers.

fields.Title: Volition: "It's the *fault* of those who *kill..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's the *fault* of those who *killed* him. Not you.

fields.Title: Half Light: "That bag's on *you*. You could have..."
fields.Dialogue Text: That bag's on *you*. You could have done something, but you just stood there. Fuck...

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Walls are full of holes in here, p..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Walls are full of holes in here, pig. Even Cuno knows that."

fields.Title: You: ""Communism is stupid, Cuno. And it'..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Communism is stupid, Cuno. And it's not a person. It's an ideology."

fields.Title: You: ""Nothing.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Nothing."

fields.Title: You: ""We should check Klaasje's room.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "We should check Klaasje's room."
fields.Alternate1: "We should check Mrs. Katarzine Alasije's room."
fields.Alternate2: "We should check Miss Oranje Disco Dancer's room."

fields.Title: You: ""All right. Saddle up." (Accept the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "All right. Saddle up." (Accept the Cuno.)

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "Look at him. Life hasn't been easy..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Look at him. Life hasn't been easy on him. You wanna drag him along and put him through more shit? *Your* shit?

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Sorry for what?! For not adding Cu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sorry for what?! For not adding Cuno to your shitshow?! Cuno's not sorry. Cuno's glad. I was just kidding. You couldn't get Cuno for a million reál. You can't even get out bed, loser."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Bitch next door? That's what Cuno'..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Bitch next door? That's what Cuno's thinking too," he agrees. "Good call. Let's rock it, pig-man."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""They say you burned half the city..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "They say you burned half the city down. Thousands dead. That's very cool to Cuno. I thought I'd stick around."

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "He's saying *I* now? And not callin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He's saying *I* now? And not calling you a f****t or a pig? Is he ill or something?

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Pretty fucking bad, Cuno thinks."..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Pretty fucking bad, Cuno thinks." He points to your left leg. "But you're one lucky pig. The doc took the bullet out and said you'll live."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno did.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno did."

fields.Title: You: "(Get up -- slowly.)"
fields.Dialogue Text: (Get up -- slowly.)

fields.Title: Cuno: "He looks you in the eye and repeats..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He looks you in the eye and repeats: "Two days is *nothing* to the Cuno."

fields.Title: Volition: "Of course she's *really* gone, what..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Of course she's *really* gone, what did you think.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Was nothin'." He tries to shake of..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Was nothin'." He tries to shake off the image. "Cuno's gonna go into a bag too. We all are."

fields.Title: Volition: "Relax, the kid is just messing with..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Relax, the kid is just messing with you. You didn't actually get *thousands* of people killed.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Tough shit, pig." He crosses his a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Tough shit, pig." He crosses his arms. "All Cuno knows is the harbour is in lockdown, town's fucked now. Half the Hardie bitches are dead and even your company bitch left."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Oh really?" He doesn't seem to bel..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh really?" He doesn't seem to believe you. "You can't get to that fat fuck Evrart anymore, 'cause the harbour's locked down. Half the Hardie bitches are dead and your company bitch sailed off."

fields.Title: You: ""Okay.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay."

fields.Title: You: ""It's simple, Cuno. I have to find..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's simple, Cuno. I have to find *communism*. Communism killed the hanged man."

fields.Title: You: ""The coolest, Cuno. But unfortunate..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The coolest, Cuno. But unfortunately it's an ideology, not a person."

fields.Title: You: ""I don't know. Let's just aimlessly..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't know. Let's just aimlessly wander until a clue presents itself."

fields.Title: You: ""Sorry, Cuno, I can't take you with..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sorry, Cuno, I can't take you with me." (Refuse the Cuno.)

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah, that's what Cuno's fuckin' s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, that's what Cuno's fuckin' saying, piggo. He's letting you off the hook." He rests his hands on his hips and looks you in the eye. "A one time boon, from Cunn to pig. There won't be a next one."

fields.Title: You: ""Wait... what?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Wait... what?"

fields.Title: You: ""The what? Where did they take him?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "The what? Where did they take him?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Nah, Cuno's just lying to you. The..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Nah, Cuno's just lying to you. The fucking boo-boo wagon took four-eyes away. He's probably gonna live."

fields.Title: You: ""What happened to me?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What happened to me?"

fields.Title: Logic: "*Babybeard*... that can only be Gar..."
fields.Dialogue Text: *Babybeard*... that can only be Garte, the cafeteria manager.

fields.Title: Endurance: "Through tears and blood and stitche..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Through tears and blood and stitches tearing it *should* be possible. From time to time...

fields.Title: You: ""Has anyone from my station been to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Has anyone from my station been to see me?"

fields.Title: You: ""You said thousands are dead?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You said thousands are dead?"
fields.Alternate1: "You said half the town is dead?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Sure, pig. Sure." He shakes his he..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sure, pig. Sure." He shakes his head. "You better have more than some fuckin' roses if you wanna bust this."

fields.Title: You: ""All right. Saddle up." (Accept the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "All right. Saddle up." (Accept the Cuno.)

fields.Title: You: ""Now? As to what's going to happen..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Now? As to what's going to happen next..."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""That sounds like a hella shit plan..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "That sounds like a hella shit plan. You askin' Cuno to come along to your shit-show and you don't even know what to do? Fuckin' check your pig journal or something. C'mon..."

fields.Title: You: ""Thanks, Cuno, you're a life saver.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Thanks, Cuno, you're a life saver."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Titus died," he says indifferently..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Titus died," he says indifferently. "Some of his goons too. The whole fucking harbour is in lockdown right now. Even Cuno can't get in."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""No." The kid suddenly looks very y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No." The kid suddenly looks very young and small. "She was dead when the Union doctor arrived. Cuno saw them put her in a bag."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Will-pig." He nods. "You ready to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Will-pig." He nods. "You ready to walk, will-pig?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Shit ain't nothing to Cuno," he sa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Shit ain't nothing to Cuno," he says with a nod. "What now?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""That's Klaasje, right? Bitch next..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "That's Klaasje, right? Bitch next door? Cuno's thinking the same thing," he agrees. "Let's rock it, pig-man."

fields.Title: You: ""Wait, but *why* do you forgive me?"
fields.Dialogue Text: "Wait, but *why* do you forgive me?

fields.Title: Empathy: "He doesn't have anyone in the world..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He doesn't have anyone in the world.

fields.Title: You: ""You said there was a doctor who re..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You said there was a doctor who removed the bullet from my leg."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Final-style," he repeats. "You fuc..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Final-style," he repeats. "You fucked everything up. Now Cuno's all you got. Terminal Cuno."

fields.Title: You: ""Is Titus alright?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Is Titus alright?"

fields.Title: Drama: "He's telling the truth."
fields.Dialogue Text: He's telling the truth.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Rich bitch? Yeah, probably. Boat's..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Rich bitch? Yeah, probably. Boat's gone. Cuno'd be fucking *fine* too if Cuno had a boat..."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah? What? What bells?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah? What? What bells?"

fields.Title: You: ""They were on the roof. I did not....."
fields.Dialogue Text: "They were on the roof. I did not... I did not catch them. Fucking butterfingers..."

fields.Title: You: ""*Why* do you wanna come with me?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "*Why* do you wanna come with me?"

fields.Title: You: ""Gnhhhh...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Gnhhhh..."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno can see you're trying to shit..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno can see you're trying to shit him, but Cuno's unshittable, so fuck does Cuno care?"

fields.Title: Logic: "If he did triage and left, you must..."
fields.Dialogue Text: If he did triage and left, you must be relatively stable.

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "Also, it's just close enough to end..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Also, it's just close enough to endure the walk.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Two days," he says indifferently...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Two days," he says indifferently. "Cuno's been out longer, sleepin' off the speed train. Two days is nothing."

fields.Title: Logic: "Evrart probably used this armed alt..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Evrart probably used this armed altercation as an excuse to completely barricade himself in the harbour and cut off all communications with the outside world.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""To the hospital, fucktard. Try to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "To the hospital, fucktard. Try to keep up with Cuno." He glares at you with something akin to respect...

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Pretty fucking bad, Cuno thinks."..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Pretty fucking bad, Cuno thinks." He points to your left leg. "But you're one lucky pig. The doc took the bullet out and said you'll live."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""The shoulder's fine, probably... T..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The shoulder's fine, probably... The doc didn't seem too worried about it -- said the bullet went right through."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""*Why* in the name of fuck would Cu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "*Why* in the name of fuck would Cuno be hurt?" The kid rolls his eyes at you.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno's fucking smart, Cuno wasn't..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno's fucking smart, Cuno wasn't *in* that fuck-pile. Cuno knows when shit goes south, unlike you."

fields.Title: You: ""I'm very bad, Cuno. Things are ver..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm very bad, Cuno. Things are very bad."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah, she's way gone pig. Cuno's b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, she's way gone pig. Cuno's been here for two days and babybeard and you are the only fucks in the building."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""You want Cuno to be your yes-man,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You want Cuno to be your yes-man, or you want me to tell it like it is? Walls are full of holes here, pig. Even Cuno knows that."

fields.Title: You: ""How long was I out?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "How long was I out?"

fields.Title: You: ""Relax, Cuno -- I know what to do.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Relax, Cuno -- I know what to do."

fields.Title: You: "(Yank it out and show the dried flo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: (Yank it out and show the dried flower, while it falls to pieces.) "This flower, Cuno!"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah that sounds real to Cuno. For..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah that sounds real to Cuno. Forensics-shit. True crime shit." The kid punches his palm. "Let's check out some crime scenes and assess shit. Pig-style! Anything else?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""So... you're gonna go after this *..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "So... you're gonna go after this *Communism*, or you wanna bounce something else off the Cuno?"

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "Ouch, ouch... The kid turns double..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Ouch, ouch... The kid turns double for a second. Damn, that hurts. Breathe...

fields.Title: You: ""Titus is dead...?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Titus is dead...?"

fields.Title: You: ""Do you know if Klaasje -- the blon..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Do you know if Klaasje -- the blonde next door -- is really gone?"

fields.Title: Shivers: "A gust of wind blows in from the ba..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A gust of wind blows in from the bay, the duraluminium box around you vibrates imperceptibly... a familiar cold, a red thread on the roof upstairs. Taut. Plucked like a string by the gust.

fields.Title: You: ""What happened to the others?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What happened to the others?"

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "He's wrong! What does he even know?..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He's wrong! What does he even know?!

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Huh?" The kid appears to be thinki..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Huh?" The kid appears to be thinking. "That could've been there for years. Cuno thinks it's a dead end."

fields.Title: You: ""I don't know but I won't give up,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't know but I won't give up, Cuno."

fields.Title: Empathy: "Look, this might be his only way ou..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Look, this might be his only way out.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah, Cuno's letting you off the h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, Cuno's letting you off the hook, piggo." He rests his hands on his hips and looks you straight in the eye. "It's a one time boon, from Cunn to pig. The next time you're a dead man."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Now's not the time to shit the bed..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Now's not the time to shit the bed, pig." He spits. "C'mon, baconman, Cuno's gonna help you hold your shit in."

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "You can take it. Just don't lean on..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You can take it. Just don't lean on the old leg too heavily.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""What?" He studies your expression...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What?" He studies your expression. "You don't believe the Cuno? You don't believe the Cuno knows this shit? Fuck you, Cuno keeps tabs. Bitch is outta town."

fields.Title: You: ""Yeah, it probably is.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, it probably is."

fields.Title: Logic: "There is no telling *when* it was m..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There is no telling *when* it was made. He had a point there.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Some of those Union goons got fuck..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Some of those Union goons got fucked," he says pointing at the door. "Now the whole harbour is in lockdown. Even Cuno can't get in there."

fields.Title: You: ""Did Elizabeth -- the gardener -- s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Did Elizabeth -- the gardener -- survive?"

fields.Title: You: ""Thanks for telling me, Cuno." (Con..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Thanks for telling me, Cuno." (Conclude.)

fields.Title: Endurance: "Say what you will, but this kid's *..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Say what you will, but this kid's *hard shit*. He might actually make a good cop one day.

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "You can barely hear him, the pain i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You can barely hear him, the pain is so bad.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""They say you got a lot of people k..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "They say you got a lot of people killed. Like half the town. They say you didn't do shit." He looks down. "I guess that's cool, so I thought I'd stick around."

fields.Title: You: ""C'mon, man... who *really* did it?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "C'mon, man... who *really* did it?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah... Some cunt from your statio..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah... Some cunt from your station came over and knife fucked you, when you were sleeping."

fields.Title: Cuno: "Cuno observes you getting on your f..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Cuno observes you getting on your feet and says nothing.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno's got zero patience for this..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno's got zero patience for this weepy shit. Cuno's been through way worse than this."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""So how is it?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "So how is it?"

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "Let's do this tango, pig, he thinks..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Let's do this tango, pig, he thinks. Detective Pig and detective Cunn on the case. We bouncin'.

fields.Title: You: ""The fuck Cuno?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "The fuck Cuno?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""No problem. Cuno shares the info.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "No problem. Cuno shares the info."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""She's gone, pig. Cuno saw her take..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "She's gone, pig. Cuno saw her take off before you started all that violent shit. Had a suitcase and shit."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""C'mon, pig..." The kid snaps his f..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "C'mon, pig..." The kid snaps his fingers. "Thoughts didn't kill Cuno's gimp. It was a person. Even Cuno can figure this shit out."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""This scene is dead." He gestures t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "This scene is dead." He gestures towards the window. "Cuno's outta here -- might as well be a pig, big-up fucky-fingers on my way out."

fields.Title: You: ""Now... as to what's going to happe..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Now... as to what's going to happen next..." (Get up.)

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Don't get all hung up on that yest..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Don't get all hung up on that yesterday's shit, piggo," the kid says, trying to sound mature. "That was then, this is now. Cuno's all about being in the moment."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Sure, Cuno's gonna help you with t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sure, Cuno's gonna help you with that. Cuno's in a *giving* mood right now."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Are your legs attached to Cuno? Ca..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Are your legs attached to Cuno? Can the *Cuno* move your legs? The fuck should I know..."

fields.Title: Savoir Faire: "You won't be able to dance much, th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You won't be able to dance much, that's for sure. But you should be able to live with limping around. If you can call that a life.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""You askin' Cuno to come along to y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You askin' Cuno to come along to your shit-show and you don't even know what to do? Fuckin' check your pig journal or something. C'mon..."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah, that's what Cuno said. No on..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, that's what Cuno said. No one goes in or out. Shit's paranoid now."

fields.Title: You: ""There's something creeping around..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "There's something creeping around out there. I sense it."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Miracle? Shit... What is this weak..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Miracle? Shit... What is this weak shit? You gotta watch your own back, miracles don't fuckin' happen in Martinaise. Get real."

fields.Title: You: ""I'm giving up. Time to start drink..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm giving up. Time to start drinking."

fields.Title: Empathy: "Asking for something -- even asking..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Asking for something -- even asking to come along -- doesn't come easy for him.

fields.Title: You: "Whatever it takes. [Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: Whatever it takes. [Leave.]

fields.Title: You: ""Didn't you say you and I were done..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Didn't you say you and I were done. Professionally?"
fields.Alternate1: "How come you're here, Cuno -- aren't you pissed at me anymore?"

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: (Variable["yard.cuno_locked_yourself_out_of_cuno_in_his_post_cunoesse_gunpointing_greeting"] == true  or  (Variable["TASK.make_truce_with_Cuno"] == true  and  Variable["TASK.make_truce_with_Cuno_done"] == false)  or  Variable["yard.cuno_befriend_lost_to_cunoesse"] == true)  and  Variable["whirling.cuno_posttribunal_talked_about_your_animosity_and_made_up"] == false

fields.Title: Drama: "Sire, the boy believes this to be t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Sire, the boy believes this to be true. He's giving you a last chance.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Just kidding, piggo," he chuckles...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Just kidding, piggo," he chuckles. "The boo-boo wagon took the binoclard away. He's probably gonna live."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""They say you shot that fucker in t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "They say you shot that fucker in the face. That's fucking cool to Cuno." He looks down. "So I thought I'd stick around."

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "Sounds like he's alright after all."
fields.Dialogue Text: Sounds like he's alright after all.

fields.Title: You: ""What happened to my room?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What happened to my room?"

fields.Title: You: ""Can I... walk?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Can I... walk?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""It's cool." He nods seriously. "Ju..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's cool." He nods seriously. "Just remember -- Cuno doesn't save shit for free."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Shit..." He shakes his head, disap..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Shit..." He shakes his head, disappointed. "Playing the Cuno like that... You better have something else for me."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""You're starting to lose the Cuno."..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're starting to lose the Cuno." He's looking around. "Sounds like you ain't got shit to go by here."

fields.Title: You: ""Sorry, Cuno, I can't take you with..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sorry, Cuno, I can't take you with me." (Refuse the Cuno.)

fields.Title: Hand/Eye Coordination: "Kid would make a half-decent sharps..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Kid would make a half-decent sharpshooter, no?

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Sorry for what?! For not adding Cu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sorry for what?! For not adding Cuno to your shitshow?! Cuno's not sorry. Cuno's glad. I was just kidding too. You couldn't get Cuno for million reál. Fuck you, okay?"

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "He's not saying Cuno -- he's saying..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He's not saying Cuno -- he's saying *I*? And not calling you a f****t or a pig? Is he ill or something?

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Listen-listen, Cuno's just big lik..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Listen-listen, Cuno's just big like that. Doesn't need that bitch-ass melodrama. Cuno fires and forgets. Cuno forgives and moves on."

fields.Title: You: ""Be straight with me. I need to get..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Be straight with me. I need to get my bearings."

fields.Title: You: ""My... disco days are done.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "My... disco days are done."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Go easy, pig. You wanna lean on th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Go easy, pig. You wanna lean on the Cuno or something?"

fields.Title: Logic: "There were only ten people present..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There were only ten people present at the fight. Ten times more than that is very unlikely.

fields.Title: You: ""You mean Garte?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You mean Garte?"

fields.Title: Volition: "Who would have thought? Perhaps you..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Who would have thought? Perhaps you should have *arrested* her?

fields.Title: You: ""You don't... know?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You don't... know?"

fields.Title: You: ""But... I don't know either.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "But... I don't know either."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno thinks you're fucked," he con..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno thinks you're fucked," he concludes with a solemn nod. "But I can help you. What'cha got? Bounce that shit off Cuno."

fields.Title: You: ""There were some footprints in the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "There were some footprints in the dust in the room behind Klaasje's..."

fields.Title: You: ""There's a... 28% possibility the v..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "There's a... 28% possibility the victim was shot from a distance."

fields.Title: You: ""There was a hole in Klaasje's wall..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "There was a hole in Klaasje's wall -- someone was checking her out. Peeping."

fields.Title: You: ""It's not *that* cool. And it's not..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's not *that* cool. And it's not a person, but an ideology."

fields.Title: You: "Say nothing."
fields.Dialogue Text: Say nothing.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""What, you mute now? Are you *ready..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What, you mute now? Are you *ready to walk*?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""So, listen, pig..." The kid seems..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "So, listen, pig..." The kid seems hesitant suddenly. "Cuno's been thinkin' about shit and, uh... Cuno's coming with you. Help you wrap this shit up. Final-style."

fields.Title: Authority: "Trying to recruit him is like tryin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Trying to recruit him is like trying to make a pet out of fire. This kid recognizes only one authority -- his own.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Coinslot's dead.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Coinslot's dead."

fields.Title: You: ""Hold on... There's something diffe..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Hold on... There's something different about you, Cuno..."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Being off speed makes Cuno sad. Ma..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Being off speed makes Cuno sad. Makes Cuno *think* about shit." He makes vague gestures around his head with his fingers.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""How would Cuno know? Cuno's not a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "How would Cuno know? Cuno's not a fucking doctor." He looks at you like you're an idiot.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""You got shot in the shoulder too,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You got shot in the shoulder too, but luckily you were wearing that fancy teapot and it took the hit for you."

fields.Title: Endurance: "With considerable pain, and a stitc..."
fields.Dialogue Text: With considerable pain, and a stitch tearing every now and then, you should be able to do it.

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "Nix Gottlieb, station medic, throws..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Nix Gottlieb, station medic, throws a bag containing a small bullet into the medical waste disposer. Then he pops some caramel candy into his mouth and says: "Next." There's a line behind his door...

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah, fuckin' dead. Died in the ho..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, fuckin' dead. Died in the hospital, I hear. Union's all weepy and shit..." He gives you a nod of acknowledgement: "It's probably your fault."

fields.Title: Logic: "You did mention doing more ballisti..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You did mention doing more ballistics...

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Accepted the Cuno like a motherfuc..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Accepted the Cuno like a motherfucker..." He nods respectfully. "What are we gonna do now?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah, debrief Cuno. Let Cuno know..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, debrief Cuno. Let Cuno know *the plan*." The kid rubs his hands together.

fields.Title: You: ""How badly am I hurt?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "How badly am I hurt?"

fields.Title: Savoir Faire: "Your balance is *way* off. You feel..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Your balance is *way* off. You feel like you're about to fall over.

fields.Title: Visual Calculus: "Ballistics. In Klaasje's room. Do i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Ballistics. In Klaasje's room. Do it *properly*.

fields.Title: You: ""Do you know if Klaasje -- the blon..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Do you know if Klaasje -- the blonde next door -- is alright?"

fields.Title: You: ""No, Cuno -- *somehow* this *is* co..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No, Cuno -- *somehow* this *is* connected to the case."

fields.Title: You: ""I don't know.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't know."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno just told you your friend is..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno just told you your friend is dead! And you're crying about pain? That doesn't seem right to Cuno." He shakes his head. "The binoclard was alright, he didn't deserve that shit..."

fields.Title: You: ""Go away, Cuno... Let me die in pea..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Go away, Cuno... Let me die in peace."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""You tore some shit up there, pig."..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You tore some shit up there, pig." Cuno is looking at you like a tamed wolf would look at his master. Like an equal. "Got shot too."

fields.Title: Cuno: "Then his expression mellows. "Cuno..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Then his expression mellows. "Cuno thinks you got shot twice. In the shoulder and in the leg. The leg's pretty fucking nasty, but a doctor looked you over and took the bullet out."

fields.Title: Volition: "You can walk. If it's possible, the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You can walk. If it's possible, then by pure willpower alone. You're a psycholocomotor.

fields.Title: You: ""Do you know who treated me, Cuno?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Do you know who treated me, Cuno?"

fields.Title: Perception (Sight): "Still, you see something akin to re..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Still, you see something akin to respect in his eyes.

fields.Title: Volition: "Thank god, okay, he's alive."
fields.Dialogue Text: Thank god, okay, he's alive.

fields.Title: You: ""She escaped?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "She escaped?"

fields.Title: Suggestion: "He's genuinely impressed, but that'..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He's genuinely impressed, but that's mostly to do with how scientific that percentage sounded.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah, it was a fucking massacre,"..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, it was a fucking massacre," Cuno says with a wide grin. "You and Cuno are the only ones left here."

fields.Title: Logic: "Doesn't sound like she's planning t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Doesn't sound like she's planning to come back.

fields.Title: Empathy: "Tough he may be, but this image lef..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Tough he may be, but this image left a mark.

fields.Title: You: ""The fucking *May bells*, Cuno, the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The fucking *May bells*, Cuno, the flowers!"

fields.Title: You: ""The miracle hasn't happened yet. I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The miracle hasn't happened yet. It's not over yet."

fields.Title: You: ""I can suddenly see how it's hard t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I can suddenly see how it's hard to indict someone who is not actually a person, but an ideology..."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Fuck off, Cuno's not into this old..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fuck off, Cuno's not into this old man piss-drinker shit." There's a short pause as he shakes his head. "You ready to walk now?"

fields.Title: Logic: "He is streetwise. Knows the neighbo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He is streetwise. Knows the neighbourhood. Knows the people. He could be useful.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yes, gimp... ?" Cuno asks, seeing..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes, gimp... ?" Cuno asks, seeing the effort it takes you to stand. "What are you gonna do now? Ride outta here on your shit-river? You'll die alone. Cuno doesn't give a shit now. Too late now. Cuno's gonna hang here and *fuck* your room up again..."

fields.Title: You: "Say nothing."
fields.Dialogue Text: Say nothing.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah... you got lucky there, pig...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah... you got lucky there, pig. Maybe now Cuno can show you what real brutal hard music is."

fields.Title: Reaction Speed: "He's really been keeping tabs -- on..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He's really been keeping tabs -- on you, the Hardies, even the company rep.

fields.Title: You: ""The whole harbour is in lockdown?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "The whole harbour is in lockdown?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""The fuck you askin' Cuno for?" He..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The fuck you askin' Cuno for?" He seems annoyed somehow. "How would Cuno know? Cuno's fucking twelve!"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Fuck, pig..." He looks at you with..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fuck, pig..." He looks at you with a worried glance. "Cuno doesn't know about this flower shit. Cuno's not feelin' it."

fields.Title: Reaction Speed: "*I* again. Something in him *is* sh..."
fields.Dialogue Text: *I* again. Something in him *is* shifting, changing.

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "Khm... DRUG ASSET DETECTED!"
fields.Dialogue Text: Khm... DRUG ASSET DETECTED!

fields.Title: Empathy: "Wow, he did not take that rejection..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Wow, he did not take that rejection well.

fields.Title: Cuno: "Cuno lets out a whistle. "That's pr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Cuno lets out a whistle. "That's pretty cool to Cuno. Cuno's also a psycho."

fields.Title: Logic: "He didn't."
fields.Dialogue Text: He didn't.

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "We're detecting *drouamine* in your..."
fields.Dialogue Text: We're detecting *drouamine* in your bloodstream. It's a potent morphine-based painkiller. The good doctor must have given you some... It's gonna suck when it wears off.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah, fuckin' babybeard. Cleaned a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, fuckin' babybeard. Cleaned all your shit up. He's like your fuckin' mom now or something."

fields.Title: You: ""What do you think I should do now,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What do you think I should do now, Cuno?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""There are fuckin' footprints *ever..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "There are fuckin' footprints *everywhere*, pig. Pigs are too into this footprints shit..." He shakes his head. "Cuno just saw footprints outside on the *sidewalk*."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Is that like a fucking street name..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Is that like a fucking street name or something?" The kid stops to think. "It's pretty cool to Cuno."

fields.Title: You: ""I'm ready, Cuno." (Conclude.)"
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm ready, Cuno." (Conclude.)

fields.Title: Volition: "This is a twelve year old kid. You..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is a twelve year old kid. You can't seriously be considering *taking him along*?! What's gonna happen to him?

fields.Title: Empathy: "Wow... the kid's name must be Cuno...."
fields.Dialogue Text: Wow... the kid's name must be Cuno. And he's about to take pity on you.

fields.Title: You: ""So we're cool now?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "So we're cool now?"

fields.Title: You: ""No... no, no...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "No... no, no..."

fields.Title: Logic: "The bullet must have passed through..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The bullet must have passed through your shoulder blade, missing your lung and your heart. You lucky son of a bitch...

fields.Title: Cuno: ""You keep asking all this *weird sh..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You keep asking all this *weird shit* from Cuno that the Cuno has no way of knowing about."
